item.title: Starblaster still around?
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

[quote=“sonny bill 9, post:20, topic:153151”]unless a mod pms a admin, admin pms admin or the other way round i dont think they will reply
ps. last active : October 10, 2007, 04:38:37 PM[/quote]
That’s not true at all. I’m sure the staff are happy to reply to reasonable messages. However most, if not all, messages are either stupid, asking for personal 1 on 1 help (when they joined like 5 minutes ago), or written in such a manner that tells us they don’t give a shit.
And really, why should we respond to messages if they’re unreadable, or demanding our undivided attention when the person making the demands is brand new?
Send a reasonable message, and you’ll get a reasonable reply.
